.Dd $Mdocdate: September 16 2014 $
.Dt MAIL.MAILDIR 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm mail.maildir
.Nd store mail in a maildir
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm mail.maildir
.Op Fl d Ar maildir
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
reads the standard input up to an end-of-file and adds it to the
provided mail directory.
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl d Ar maildir
Specify the path to user mail directory.
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std mail.maildir
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr mail 1 ,
.Xr smtpd 8
@
